An enum that defines types of GPUs.

Example:
    ```python
    from beta9 import GpuType, function

    @function(gpu=GpuType.T4)
    def some_func()
        print("I will run on a T4 gpu!")

    # This is equivalent to the above ^
    @function(gpu="T4")
    def some_other_func()
        print("I will run on a T4 gpu!")
    ```
